description: Details of condition 8 part 'a' and 'b' (Site Investigation) for Phase 2 Parcel 3 only required by planning permission 16/AP/2740 for 'Demolition of existing ward buildings and nurses accommodation and development of site to provide a new secondary school within the retained and refurbished 'Chateau' building fronting East Dulwich Grove  and in a series of new buildings and extensions up to 5 storeys high, comprising teaching and administration spaces, dining and indoor sports hall, multi-use games area, accesses, car parking and servicing areas and landscaping (Use Class D1)'.
